com.hazelcast.concurrent.lock

Class LockStoreProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.concurrent.lock.LockStoreProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LockStore

    public final class LockStoreProxy
extends Object
implements LockStore
    Proxy to a LockStoreImpl. Since a LockStoreImpl may be destroyed upon service reset (eg. after a split-brain is healed), some of this proxy's methods employ get-or-create to locate the LockStoreImpl or get-or-null when creation of the LockStoreImpl is not required and its absence is interpreted as "no lock exists".
